ist\u2013Leninist)(Dominican Republic)|Communist Party (Marxist\u2013Leninist)]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Donetsk People's Republic}} (unrecognized country) \u2013 [[Communist Party of the Donetsk People's Republic]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|East Timor}} \u2013 [[Socialist Party of Timor]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Ecuador}} \u2013 [[Communist Party of Ecuador]], [[Marxist\u2013Leninist Communist Party of Ecuador]], [[Workers' Party of Ecuador]], [[Democratic People's Movement]], [[Communist Party of Ecuador \u2013 Red Sun]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Egypt}} \u2013 [[Egyptian Communist Party]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|El Salvador}} \u2013 [[Communist Party of El Salvador]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Ethiopia}} \u2013 [[All-Ethiopia Socialist Movement]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Finland}} \u2013 [[Communist Party of Finland (1997)|Communist Party of Finland]], [[Communist Workers' Party \u2013 For Peace and Socialism]], [[League of Communists (Finland)|League of Communists]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|France}} \u2013 [[French Communist Party]], [[Pole of Communist Rebirth in France]], [[Workers' Communist Party of France]], [[Marxist\u2013Leninist Communist Organization \u2013 Proletarian Way]], [[Revolutionary Communist Party of France]] [[Revolutionary Party - Communists]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Georgia}} \u2013 [[Communist Party of Georgia]], [[Unified Communist Party of Georgia]], [[New Communist Party of Georgia]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Germany}} \u2013 [[German Communist Party]], [[Marxist\u2013Leninist Party of Germany]], [[Communist Party of Germany (1990)|Communist Party of Germany]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Greece}} \u2013 [[Communist Party of Greece]], [[Marxist\u2013Leninist Communist Party of Greece]], [[Communist Party of Greece (Marxist\u2013Leninist