724/http://www.jlp.net/|archivedate=25 August 2013|url-status=dead|accessdate=19 March 2013}}</ref> [[Workers' Communist Party In Japan]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bekkoame.ne.jp/i/ga3129/|title=Workers' Communist Party In Japan|publisher=Workers' Communist Party In Japan|accessdate=1 April 2020}}</ref> [[Workers Socialist League (Japan)|Workers Socialist League]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Jordan}} \u2013 [[Jordanian Communist Party]], [[Jordanian Democratic People's Party]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Kazakhstan}} \u2013 [[Communist People's Party of Kazakhstan]], [[Communist Party of Kazakhstan]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Kuwait}} \u2013 [[Kuwaiti Progressive Movement]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Kenya}} \u2013 [[Communist Party of Kenya]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Kyrgyzstan}} \u2013 [[Party of Communists of Kyrgyzstan]], [[Communist Party of Kyrgyzstan]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Latvia}} \u2013 [[Socialist Party of Latvia]], [[Communist Party of Latvia]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Lebanon}} \u2013 [[Lebanese Communist Party]], [[Communist Action Organization in Lebanon]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Lesotho}} \u2013 [[Communist Party of Lesotho]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Lithuania}} \u2013 [[Socialist People's Front]], [[Communist Party of Lithuania]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Luxembourg}} \u2013 [[Communist Party of Luxembourg]], [[Communist Organization of Luxembourg]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Madagascar}} \u2013 [[Congress Party for the Independence of Madagascar]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Mali}} \u2013 [[Malian Party of Labour]], [[African Solidarity for Democracy and Independence]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Malta}} \u2013 [[Communist Party of Malta]]\n* {{flag+link|List of political parties in|Martinique}} \u2013 [[Martinican